ComicInfo.Title: Chapter One: Rabbit Pellets
ComicInfo.Series: Auntie Agatha's Home for Wayward Rabbits
ComicInfo.Summary: Auntie Agatha’s Home for Wayward Rabbits is in danger. Run by the titular Agatha and her niece, Julie, this peculiar shelter cares for damaged and dysfunctional rabbits—and now it’s being threatened by a wealthy businessman who will stop at nothing to tear it down. This charming series marks the return of critically acclaimed writer KEITH GIFFEN to creator-owned work.
